  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine if oral antibiotic treatment with CEM-102 and Rifampin is as effective and safe
      as the standard of care antibiotic therapy for the treatment of hip and knee prosthetic joint
      or spacer infections
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
